<aside class="seatmap-side seatmap-side--left stage4-tool-side">
    <div class="stage4-side-title">
        <span class="stage4-step-badge">STEP 06</span>
        <strong>최종 꾸미기</strong>
        <small>포토샵처럼 도면 위에 요소를 올려 최종 이미지를 보정합니다.</small>
    </div>

    <section class="stage4-panel stage4-panel--tools">
        <h3>도구</h3>
        <div class="stage4-tool-grid" id="stage4ToolGrid">
            <button type="button" class="stage4-tool is-active" data-tool="move" title="이동 / 선택">
                <span>↕</span><b>이동</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage4-tool" data-tool="text" title="텍스트">
                <span>T</span><b>텍스트</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage4-tool" data-tool="rect" title="사각형">
                <span>▭</span><b>박스</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage4-tool" data-tool="ellipse" title="원형">
                <span>◯</span><b>원형</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage4-tool" data-tool="line" title="선">
                <span>╱</span><b>선</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage4-tool" data-tool="seat" title="좌석 표시">
                <span>▦</span><b>좌석</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage4-tool" data-tool="stage" title="무대 박스">
                <span>ST</span><b>무대</b>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="stage4-tool" data-tool="erase" title="지우개">
                <span>⌫</span><b>지우개</b>
            </button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stage4-panel">
        <h3>빠른 추가</h3>
        <div class="stage4-quick-list">
            <button type="button" class="stage4-quick" id="addStageLabel">STAGE 라벨</button>
            <button type="button" class="stage4-quick" id="addEntranceLabel">입구 표시</button>
            <button type="button" class="stage4-quick" id="addGuideBox">안내 박스</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stage4-panel">
        <h3>브러쉬 / 도형 설정</h3>
        <div class="stage4-field-grid">
            <label>
                <span>채우기</span>
                <input type="color" id="fillColor" value="#8b5cf6">
            </label>
            <label>
                <span>선 색상</span>
                <input type="color" id="strokeColor" value="#111827">
            </label>
            <label>
                <span>글자색</span>
                <input type="color" id="textColor" value="#ffffff">
            </label>
            <label>
                <span>글자 크기</span>
                <input type="number" id="fontSize" value="22" min="8" max="96">
            </label>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stage4-panel">
        <h3>작업</h3>
        <div class="stage4-action-list">
            <button type="button" class="stage4-action stage4-action--dark" id="undoDecorate">되돌리기</button>
            <button type="button" class="stage4-action" id="clearDecorations">꾸미기 초기화</button>
            <button type="button" class="stage4-action stage4-action--green" id="saveDecoratedImage">도면 임시 저장</button>
        </div>
        <p class="stage4-help">상단 저장하기를 누르면 현재 캔버스 이미지가 함께 저장됩니다. 이 화면은 JSON 검수가 아니라 최종 이미지 보정용입니다.</p>
    </section>
</aside>

<main class="seatmap-main stage4-canvas-main">
    <div class="stage4-canvas-head">
        <div>
            <strong>최종 도면 캔버스</strong>
            <span id="stage4CanvasInfo">도면을 불러오는 중...</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stage4-canvas-head__tools">
            <button type="button" id="fitCanvasView">화면 맞춤</button>
            <button type="button" id="resetCanvasView">100%</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stage4-canvas-viewport" id="stage4CanvasViewport">
        <div class="stage4-canvas-board" id="stage4CanvasBoard">
            <canvas id="canvas"></canvas>
            <canvas id="decorateOverlay"></canvas>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<aside class="seatmap-side seatmap-side--right stage4-right-side">
    <section class="stage4-panel">
        <h3>선택 요소</h3>
        <div class="stage4-selected-box" id="selectedObjectInfo">
            아직 선택된 요소가 없습니다.
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stage4-panel">
        <h3>레이어</h3>
        <div class="stage4-layer-list" id="layerList">
            <div class="stage4-empty-layer">추가된 꾸미기 요소가 없습니다.</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stage4-panel">
        <h3>미니맵</h3>
        <div class="stage4-minimap-wrap">
            <canvas id="stage4MiniMap" width="260" height="170"></canvas>
        </div>
        <p class="stage4-help">좌측 도구를 고른 뒤 도면을 클릭하면 임시 요소가 추가됩니다.</p>
    </section>
</aside>
